title: 01_16_08_LP_LIVE_Hannover

TUI Arena
16th January 2008

01. What I&#039;ve Done
02. Faint
03. No More Sorrow
04. Somewhere I Belong
05. Lying From You
06. From The Inside
07. Points Of Authority
08. Hands Held High
09. Wake
10. Given Up
11. Valentine&#039;s Day
12. Numb
13. Just Like Heaven (The Cure cover) - named Show Me
14. Shadow Of The Day
15. Crawling
16. In The End

19. Breaking The Habit
20. A Place For My Head

Show Notes:
- This was the first time that &#039;What I&#039;ve Done&#039; has ever opened the live set, and it features a new intro as well.
- This was the first time that &#039;Valentine&#039;s Day&#039; was ever played live.
- This was the first time that &#039;A Place For My Head&#039; was played since the Sao Paulo, Brazil show on September 11th, 2004.
- This was the first time since 2004 that &#039;One Step Closer&#039; closed the set again. Awesome!
- This was also the first time ever LP played in Hannover.
- &#039;Petrified&#039; Verse 2 was over &#039;Points Of Authority&#039;. The song also featured a new outro.

Thx to lplive.net for the info
